<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1"/>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <style>
        body {
          font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          background-color: #fff;
          color: #333;
          font-size: 100%;
        }
        
        @media (max-width:450px) {
          body {
            font-size: 80%;
          }
        }
        
        h1, h2, p, button, select, input, table {
          display: block;
          width: 90%;
          max-width: 450px;
          margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        h1 {
          font-size: 4em;
          margin-top: 1.5em;
          margin-bottom: 1em;
        }
        
        p {
          font-size: 1.5em;
          margin: 1em auto;
        }
        
        button {
          margin: 2em auto;
          font-family: inherit;
          font-size: 2em;
          font-weight: bold;
          color: #eee;
          background-color: #333;
          border: none;
          padding: 0.3em 1em;
          border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        button:active {
          background-color: #666;
        }
        
        select, input {
          margin: 1em auto;
          font-size: 1.5em;
          font-family: inherit;
          border: 2px solid #333;
          border-radius: 2px;
          padding: 0.3em;
        }
        
        table {
          margin: 1em auto;
          font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        
        th {
          text-align: left;
          min-width: 50%
        }
        
        td {
          text-align: right;
          vertical-align: bottom;
        }
        
        td, th {
          border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
          padding: 0.3em 0;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Vaani Setup Step 2</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Vaani Setup</h1>
    <h2>Step 2: Evernote</h2>
    <p>
      In order for Vaani to work, it needs access to your Evernote account.
    </p>
    <form method="get" action="/oauth">
    <button>Connect to Evernote</button>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
